column5: Just dropping by to browse the action on OFC. Thought i would say a howdilly hodilly to my fishing neighboroonies.  I'll put together a season report at some point. Snag's sister keeps me on a tight leash so I have a word-limit.  Hope everyone is
Ricoh, your absence is extremely distressing LOL  How are those stripers treating you?!?  Miss ya buddy!

Doug..  Snag's sister called me the other night, she seemed real distressed..  Says you been signing her Sean Cullen tunes outside her bedroom in the wee hours..  She says that Pandas Must Die song is really starting to bug the shnikes outta her!! LOL  How ya doing douggie?  Been many moons since our last circuit..  Doncha love me no more?!  Ric!  Coming up to NY the weekend of the 12th... wondering if ya wanted to link for a yankee's game?!  gimme yo numba!  HD
Hey Doug! Was wondering what happened to you. Tried to call you to go fishin but your number is disconnected. Anyways, welcome back and looking forward to your report.
SUP Lucid? Good to see your doing good, Can't wait to see your season report.

Hey Doug,  Does my Sis' know you are here?  The only reason she keeps you on a short leash is because you gnawed through the anklets.  You'll be pleased to know that Dad sold the shot gun after the wedding.   Hey!!  Triplets that all look like Fidel?? Wats up wid dat!!!!   Thanks for keeping your account alive,  Now show us the money!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!  (better be plenty of vertical thumbs and a wet smoke in your lips!!)
....Hey Doug, where the hell you been?

We were supposed to hit the lake this morning...  My guess is he's still shnoozing..  He's likely to re-emerge again sometime next year..  Doug's had a banner smallie season though!  Sorry Doug, I gotta do it...  AAAAAAAAAAYYYYYYYEE    HD
....Well there's nothing wrong with that, is there? Perhaps you could drag his sorry ass up to Lakair Fidel? Then he could show me how to wrestle them smallies out of the west arm.
Nice to hear from you dude.
